channel.title: Cect 599?
channel.description: CECT 599? Hey, I just purchased one of these off trademe, and I'm waiting for it to come in the mail... Does anyone know anything about this like, is it worth it, is it good at music/videos, does it have wifi? (I purchased as a replacement for ipaq h6340 because the charger slot in the phone broked...) so far what i know: its a phone it has a big-ish screen it has a 1.3mp camera it takes sd (not sure if micro or normal.) it looks sort of like the iphone it has a touch screen
